<h3>MVC Processing Flow</h3>

<ol class="flow-list">
    <li>1. User sends a request to a URL.</li>

    <li>2. Controller Action receives the request.</li>

    <li>3. Controller calls Service to retrieve data.</li>

    <li>4. Controller transforms data into ViewModel.</li>

    <li>5. View uses Razor Syntax to render HTML for the browser.</li>
</ol>

